Tables
    1) stock_table (home)
        - id (stock symbol)
        - Todays Open
        - Todays Close
        - Todays High
        - Todays Low
        - Todays Average Volume
        - Todays History (collection id)
        - Overall History (collection id)
    1a) daily_stock (polled at half minute)
        - id (generated)
        -$MarketPrice
        -$Volume
        -$ShortRatio
        -$Symbol
        -$BidPrice
        -$AskPrice
        -$Time
    1b) Overall History (polled at the 15min)
        - id (generated)
        - Market Price
        - Volume
        - Short Ratio
        - Average volume to this point

